them. In the process I have supplemented my technical knowledge of Cloud computing,
VMware virtualization and countless other products but I‚Äôve also brought value to
the company by organizing and motivating various teams to perform at higher levels.
And while that has been extraordinarily challenging, it has been very rewarding.</p>

<p>So, what motivates you? While you ponder that question, I‚Äôll start writing about my experiences with
